  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist my next game - UVSU</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/8e62e195a155a3506193b310d347be20.poster.avif?t=1689710553\" width=474 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/8e62e195a155a3506193b310d347be20.webm?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/8e62e195a155a3506193b310d347be20.mp4?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Trouble Juice is a Side Scrolling Shooter Roguelike set in a TV show tournament that is broadcasted across the universe.<br>Become the ultimate champion and earn your place in the galaxy's hall of fame!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNLOCK STUFF IN THE ACHIEVEMENT BINGO!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/c785a149152b7e1375641e6eb5d98a2d.poster.avif?t=1689710553\" width=474 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/c785a149152b7e1375641e6eb5d98a2d.webm?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/c785a149152b7e1375641e6eb5d98a2d.mp4?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Clear a row, column or diagonal of achievements to unlock new juices, characters and alternate costumes!<br>Can you clear the entire board?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/c547aca2d4b2b21c7c0fbc6b9442b7f3.poster.avif?t=1689710553\" width=474 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/c547aca2d4b2b21c7c0fbc6b9442b7f3.webm?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/c547aca2d4b2b21c7c0fbc6b9442b7f3.mp4?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Easy to pick up, hard to put down.<br>Runs are short and packed with action.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/0f8b514129be758c29dc574faf175cc9.poster.avif?t=1689710553\" width=474 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/0f8b514129be758c29dc574faf175cc9.webm?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/0f8b514129be758c29dc574faf175cc9.mp4?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Buy juices from Juice Guy that upgrade your gun, mobility, health and other things.<br>Experiment with different combinations to find what's the best mix!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/c97e544091e679e5f4b3915eb8342c38.poster.avif?t=1689710553\" width=474 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/c97e544091e679e5f4b3915eb8342c38.webm?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/c97e544091e679e5f4b3915eb8342c38.mp4?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can also choose to shoot Juice Guy and get some health.<br>Don't worry, he can't die.<br>However, he will remember...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/d068de8e659b78322276a6b514127eb9.poster.avif?t=1689710553\" width=474 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/d068de8e659b78322276a6b514127eb9.webm?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065840/extras/d068de8e659b78322276a6b514127eb9.mp4?t=1689710553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Every character has their own special ability which uses the stamina bar.",
